buf.push("<p class=\"block\">Not sure about how a specific feature works? Have an idea for a new one? Got a complaint or comment? We’d like to hear from you.  Engage with us and other users via your favorite social media: <a href='https://twitter.com/beakernotebook'>Twitter</a>,\n<a href='https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook'>Github</a>,\n<a href='https://stackoverflow.com/search?q=beaker-notebook'>Stack Overflow</a>,\n<a href='https://www.facebook.com/beakernotebook'>Facebook</a>,\n<a href='https://plus.google.com/b/103696694815824084077/103696694815824084077/'>Google+</a>\nor just email\n<a href='mailto:beaker-feedback@twosigma.com'>beaker-feedback@twosigma.com</a>.  There's also a public email list for users to communicate each other, and with us the developers: <a href='https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/beaker-user'>beaker-user@googlegroups.com</a>.\n</p>");
