buf.push("<p class=\"block\">Beaker is an Open Source tool available under the Apache 2.0\nlicense. As such, we welcome developers to extend and improve it in\nways that can benefit everyone. In order for us to accept your code\nor pull request, we need for you to fill out and send back to us a signed copy of the <a href=\"cla.zip\">Contributor\nLicense Agreement</a>.\n</p><p class=\"block\">We’re also looking to expand our team, so if you’re a rock solid <a href='http://www.twosigma.com/careers/position/936.html', target=\"_blank\", onClick=\"_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Careers', 'Link', 'backendDev']);\">full stack web developer</a> or a razor sharp <a href='http://www.twosigma.com/careers/position/935.html', target=\"_blank\", onClick=\"_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Careers', 'Link', 'frontendDev']);\">front end web developer</a> and you’re interested in working on Beaker full time, check out the job descriptions and let us know.\n</p>");
