buf.push("<div class=\"releases markdown\"><h4 id=\"current-version-1-7-1-2016-11-22\">Current Version - 1.7.1 - 2016.11.22</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix closing dropdown menus <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4939\">#4939</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix yBound in plots <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4944\">#4944</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix save-as of plots with advanced styling <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4918\">#4918</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix top and bottom margins of heatmaps <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4929\">#4929</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix autotranslation for node <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4933\">#4933</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix error reporting from node <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4935\">#4935</a>.</li>\n<li>Update plotly and bokeh tutorials <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4946\">#4946</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-7-2016-11-14\">1.7 - 2016.11.14</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Support IPython v5 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4547\">#4547</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4799\">#4799</a>.</li>\n<li>New file browser <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3818\">#3818</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4810\">#4810</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4642\">#4642</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4626\">#4626</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4625\">#4625</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4613\">#4613</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4552\">#4552</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4551\">#4551</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4514\">#4514</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4513\">#4513</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4421\">#4421</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4420\">#4420</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4419\">#4419</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4343\">#4343</a>.</li>\n<li>Add find and replace <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1466\">#1466</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4803\">#4803</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4755\">#4755</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4729\">#4739</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4728\">#4728</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4727\">#4727</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4726\">#4726</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4725\">#4725</a>.</li>\n<li>Handle tables with many columns without hanging <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4682\">#4682</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4780\">#4780</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4749\">#4749</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4741\">#4741</a>.</li>\n<li>Add loadLibrary for sharing code between notebooks <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3688\">#3688</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4114\">#4114</a>.</li>\n<li>Closed cells show one-line summaries <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3159\">#3159</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4789\">#4789</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4292\">#4292</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4260\">#4260</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4259\">#4259</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4215\">#4215</a>.</li>\n<li>Recent notebooks shown on start page <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4177\">#4177</a>.</li>\n<li>Run-all progress for the top bar <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4100\">#4100</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4516\">#4516</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4508\">#4508</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3388\">#3388</a>.</li>\n<li>Add locking individual cells <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4061\">#4061</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4565\">#4565</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4501\">#4501</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4430\">#4430</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4394\">#4394</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4393\">#4393</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4154\">#4154</a>.</li>\n<li>Option to alert user on cell completion with popup and sound <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3643\">#3643</a>.</li>\n<li>Support paste and drag-and-drop of images into notebook <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3234\">#3234</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4737\">#4737</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4602\">#4602</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"docker\">Docker</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Improve Docker experience <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4720\">#4720</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4719\">#4719</a></li>\n<li>Include Pandas v0.19 in Docker container <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4858\">#4858</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4822\">#4822</a>.</li>\n<li>Docker build process avoids npm permission problem <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4824\">#4824</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"plots\">Plots</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Improve default plotting colors <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4109\">#4109</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4677\">#4677</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4676\">#4676</a>.</li>\n<li>Add advanced styling options <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/pull/4902\">#4902</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix time axis labeling in combined plots <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4214\">#4214</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix overlap between Y axis label and tick label <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4113\">#4113</a>.</li>\n<li>Improve plot tooltip API <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4213\">#4213</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4200\">#4200</a>.</li>\n<li>XYStacker handles ragged arrays <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4212\">#4212</a>.</li>\n<li>Add context-menu for saving plots as PNG or SVG <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4452\">#4452</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix box plot with one element, and avoid box plots for non-monotonic data <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4180\">#4180</a>.</li>\n<li>Add tick label visibility options <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4881\">#4881</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4894\">#4894</a>.</li>\n<li>Add legend name option for histograms <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/pull/4887\">#4887</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4891\">#4891</a>.</li>\n<li>Category plots correctly promote list to 2D-array <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4863\">#4863</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix panning of empty plots <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4418\">#4418</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix handling of upperMargin and lowerMargin plot parameters <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4115\">#4115</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix plotting tutorial to work in international locales <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4291\">#4291</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"tables\">Tables</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Make table interactions programmable <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3595\">#3595</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4320\">#4320</a>.</li>\n<li>Add API for table format control <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3596\">#3596</a>.</li>\n<li>Handle change in R type system that caused tables to appear as text <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4108\">#4108</a>.</li>\n<li>Display map as table even if keys are objects <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4110\">#4110</a>.</li>\n<li>Bar chart in table works with negative values <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3521\">#3521</a>.</li>\n<li>Table save-as CSV should encode HTML <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4838\">#4838</a>.</li>\n<li>Table export handles null cells <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4270\">#4270</a>.</li>\n<li>Add download as CSV for tables <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4482\">#4482</a>.</li>\n<li>Table download CSV fixed for Firefox, copy to clipboard fixed for Safari <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4836\">#4836</a>.</li>\n<li>Table column shifts in Firefox <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4073\">#4073</a>.</li>\n<li>Table highlight border fixed <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4526\">#4526</a>.</li>\n<li>Table column menus mispositioned after use <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4777\">#4777</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix display of Pandas tables after sort_values() <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4095\">#4095</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix handling of timedelta columns in tables <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4574\">#4574</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix alignment of table with one column <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4311\">#4311</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix selecting text from table column search field <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4263\">#4263</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"math\">Math</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Support KaTeX v0.6 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4055\">#4055</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved error handling from TeX <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3203\">#3203</a>.</li>\n<li>Correctly highlight TeX and JS that are embedded in text cells <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3280\">#3280</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix math inside of backquotes <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1427\">#1427</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"node\">Node</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Node supports autotranslation <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4267\">#4267</a>.</li>\n<li>Node supports loading modules with require <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4092\">#4092</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4077\">#4077</a>.</li>\n<li>Node supports using variables from one cell in another <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4068\">#4068</a>.</li>\n<li>Node now handles % operator <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2979\">#2979</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"python\">Python</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix colored output from Python magic shell commands <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4089\">#4089</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix Python2 autotranslation of unicode <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4675\">#4675</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix Python2 table display with unicode <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4673\">#4673</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix Python autotranslation of date timezones <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4172\">#4172</a>.</li>\n<li>Add ability to delete and test values in beaker object in Python <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3822\">#3822</a>.</li>\n<li>Better display of errors during initialization of Python <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4333\">#4333</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4334\">#4334</a>.</li>\n<li>Do not rerun Python setup code when reconnecting to a session <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4315\">#4315</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"other-languages\">Other Languages</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Support Julia v0.5 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/pull/4855\">#4855</a>.</li>\n<li>Add module browser and loader to JavaScript plugin <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/429\">#429</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4042\">#4042</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4041\">#4041</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix SQL handling of comments <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4317\">#4317</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix handling of GStrings (Groovy Strings) in autotranslation <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4271\">#4271</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix handling of javax.swing.ImageIcon in autotranslation <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4052\">#4052</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix Scala on Windows <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4781\">#4781</a>.</li>\n<li>Handle nonserializeable results in Scala <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4272\">#4272</a>.</li>\n<li>Add autocomplete for Scala, upgrade to v2.11.8 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4345\">#4345</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix thread leak in JVM languages <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4112\">#4112</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"keyboard-handling\">Keyboard Handling</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Add :w and :wq and :q commands to vim mode <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4284\">#4284</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4870\">#4870</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix cmd box in vim mode <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4283\">#4283</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix page up/down keys when editing code <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4628\">#4628</a>.</li>\n<li>On mac in emacs mode, fix control-N <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4772\">#4772</a>.</li>\n<li>Add keybinding to cancel cell execution (control-C on Mac, alt-C on windows) <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4412\">#4412</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4480\">#4480</a>.</li>\n<li>Add keybinding to raise or lower section levels <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4338\">#4338</a>.</li>\n<li>Add keybinding Cmd-shift-U inserts code cell above <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4294\">#4294</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4328\">#4328</a>.</li>\n<li>Add keybinding Cmd-shift-Y to insert a text cell <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4277\">#4277</a>.</li>\n<li>Add keyboard navigation of language manager <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3856\">#3856</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix behavior of Cmd-shift-A in text cell <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4276\">#4276</a>.</li>\n<li>Shift-enter only advances to next cell after evaluation succeeds <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4411\">#4411</a>.</li>\n<li>Shift-enter creates new cell when used on last cell <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4282\">#4282</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix cmd-shift-E in advanced mode <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4416\">#4416</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"miscellaneous\">Miscellaneous</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>False values are now shown <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4088\">#4088</a>.</li>\n<li>GridOutputContainerLayoutManager defaults to two columns <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4198\">#4198</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix JavaScript cell handling of null result <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4605\">#4605</a>.</li>\n<li>HTML cells support template expansion like text cells <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4546\">#4546</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4584\">#4584</a>.</li>\n<li>EasyForm date picker accepts java date not just string <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4856\">#4857</a>.</li>\n<li>Work with new Beaker Lab publication server URL format <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4846\">#4846</a>.</li>\n<li>Start page button reacts to narrow window <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4622\">#4622</a>.</li>\n<li>Long filename breaks start page <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4515\">#4515</a>.</li>\n<li>Autocomplete improved <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4553\">#4553</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4700\">#4700</a>.</li>\n<li>Various edits should mark notebook as dirty <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4385\">#4385</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4377\">#4377</a>.</li>\n<li>Mark notebook dirty sooner when editing text cells <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4378\">#4378</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4739\">#4739</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix performance bug when typing into section headers and text cells <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4909\">#4909</a>.</li>\n<li>Added hysteresis to submenu closing <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4740\">#4740</a>.</li>\n<li>Keep submenus open when mouse leaves <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4702\">#4702</a>.</li>\n<li>Avoid restarting nginx <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4707\">#4707</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4845\">#4845</a>.</li>\n<li>Indicate errors even when section is closed <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4910\">#4910</a>.</li>\n<li>Printing vastly improved <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4153\">#4153</a>.</li>\n<li>Add show/hide toggle to text cells <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4265\">#4265</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix formatting of progress display <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4464\">#4464</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4370\">#4370</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4357\">#4357</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4350\">#4350</a>.</li>\n<li>Wrap text output <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4161\">#4161</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4280\">#4280</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4266\">#4266</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix cursor in cell output menu <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4538\">#4538</a>.</li>\n<li>Reorganize items in cell menu <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4512\">#4512</a>.</li>\n<li>Run button should blur during evaluation <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4253\">#4253</a>.</li>\n<li>When text cells are inserted they get focus ready to type <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4250\">#4250</a>.</li>\n<li>Clicking link in text cell opens new tab <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4249\">#4249</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix shifting of document when modal dialogs appear <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4225\">#4225</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix shadow on cell border in ambiance theme <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4137\">#4137</a>.</li>\n<li>Make the gray used for code font and quote bar easier to see <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4118\">#4118</a>.</li>\n<li>Better handle error of unknown language when a notebook is opened <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4221\">#4221</a>.</li>\n<li>Error text should be in red in ambiance theme <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4550\">#4550</a>.</li>\n<li>Improve error reporting if you open a JSON file that is not a Beaker notebook <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4471\">#4471</a>.</li>\n<li>Notebook path easier to select <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4616\">#4616</a>.</li>\n<li>Provide better default title for publication <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4634\">#4634</a>.</li>\n<li>Hashmap with null key crashes serializer <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4820\">#4820</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved error handling during serialization <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4783\">#4783</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix closing a notebook from the start page while it is still open in another tab <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4379\">#4379</a>.</li>\n<li>Provide access to version string via beaker object <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2097\">#2097</a>.</li>\n<li>Use SLF4J for all logging instead of printing <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4298\">#4298</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix permissions on session backup directory <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4281\">#4281</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4296\">#4296</a>.</li>\n<li>Improve documentation of emoji in text cells <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/4258\">#4258</a>.</li>\n<li>For a complete list of all 408 issues see <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed+closed%3A2016-04-22..2016-11-14\">github</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-6-2016-04-22\">1.6 - 2016.04.22</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New table UI including filtering, searching, bar charts, heat maps, tighter spacing in advanced mode, drag to resize columns, quick switching from pagination to scrolling, and menus for each column. <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2836\">#2836</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3591\">#3591</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3777\">#3777</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved autocomplete including documentation and arguments <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2831\">#2831</a>.</li>\n<li>New landing page <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3567\">#3567</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3602\">#3602</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved handling of 64-bit integers and bignums in tables and autotranslation <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3332\">#3332</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3511\">#3511</a>.</li>\n<li>New plot interaction APIs to get callbacks and trigger running cells when the user clicks on a plot <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2888\">#2888</a>.</li>\n<li>JavaScript supports ECMAScript 2015 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1625\">#1625</a>.</li>\n<li>Added JavaDoc for interal plotting, output containers, and layout manager APIs <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2632\">#2632</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3525\">#3525</a>.</li>\n<li>Can select lines with line numbers <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3233\">#3233</a>.</li>\n<li>Flattened menus for faster access <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/907\">#907</a>.</li>\n<li>Updated KaTeX to version 0.5 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3113\">#3113</a>.</li>\n<li>Dynamic loader moved to parent-first, fixing a number of class loader issues like access to Grape and Lucene <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2658\">#2658</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3612\">#3612</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2276\">#2276</a>.</li>\n<li>Added command to reset all backends and run all init cells (control-R), run all cells (F5), and other keyboard shortcuts <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3784\">#3784</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3800\">#3800</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3545\">#3545</a>.</li>\n<li>R backend can now be reset, does not loose focus on startup on Mac <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3828\">#3828</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3355\">#3355</a>.</li>\n<li>Java no longer confused by comments, errors not mangled, interfaces and static imports supported <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3768\">#3768</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3760\">#3760</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3762\">#3762</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3761\">#3761</a>.</li>\n<li>Language manager improvements: warn about closing without saving, tooltips with documentation, progress feedback during changes, API access to language settings <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2982\">#2982</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3677\">#3677</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2613\">#2613</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3727\">#3727</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3562\">#3562</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3479\">#3479</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2972\">#2972</a>.</li>\n<li>HTML cells now handle <code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> elements <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3436\">#3436</a>.</li>\n<li>Code editing changed to word-wrap by default (but you can still set any cell back to scroll with the menu) <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3423\">#3423</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3704\">#3704</a>.</li>\n<li>For a complete list of the 286 resolved issues, see <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed+closed%3A2016-01-22..2016-04-22\">github</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-5-2-2016-03-07-1-5-3-for-electron-versions-\">1.5.2 - 2016.03.07 (1.5.3 for Electron versions)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Security fix to XSRF bug <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3627\">#3627</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-5-1-2016-01-22\">1.5.1 - 2016.01.22</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>ESC or clicking away the &quot;File Exists&quot; dialog is broken <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3395\">#3395</a>.</li>\n<li>In ambiance theme, dangerous buttons should be red <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3384\">#3384</a>.</li>\n<li>Fixed CategoryLines style <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3387\">#3387</a>.</li>\n<li>Fixed Stems style <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3381\">#3381</a>.</li>\n<li>Fixed cumulative flag when normed flag set on histograms <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3407\">#3407</a>.</li>\n<li>Make logo color a parameter <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3088\">#3088</a>.</li>\n<li>Fixed plot resize thumb in ambiance theme <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3392\">#3392</a>.</li>\n<li>Fixed changing theme marks notebook as edited <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3385\">#3385</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-5-2016-01-17\">1.5 - 2016.01.17</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add a <a href=\"https://twitter.com/beakernotebook/status/682233629460795393\">light-on-dark</a> theme (ambiance) <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2830\">#2830</a>.</li>\n<li>Add <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/56841828-95ab-49ed-bd02-8965c914bbd5?fullscreen=false\">Lua/Torch</a> support <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1060\">#1060</a>.</li>\n<li>Improve <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560b4e07-6785-4cc1-95d6-bde1ab80ff8f\">Clojure</a> support, including autotranslation, autocomplete, namespaces, and require <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2475\">#2475</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2478\">#2478</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2476\">#2476</a>.</li>\n<li>Add <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560b4c5e-ace8-459d-aaf7-1e78b22dce12?fullscreen=false\">autotranslation</a> to Julia <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/815\">#815</a>.</li>\n<li>Add many native chart types (<a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/569d744e-a456-44cd-a1e4-5e3744db1869?fullscreen=true\">bar charts</a>, <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/569d7600-833d-4d95-a330-5ec8c1578b84?fullscreen=true\">histograms</a>, <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/569d770f-9949-4d84-ae1b-2087d3398448?fullscreen=true\">heat maps</a>, and <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/569d77a7-ad09-4958-ad97-eca4316695a9?fullscreen=true\">tree maps</a>).</li>\n<li>Support NanoPlots with nanosecond resolution (64-bit integers in in this circumstance JS).</li>\n<li>Layout Managers for <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/56947b5d-26f2-4c79-9a1d-17e4912f7734\">Output Containers</a> (columns, tabbed, cycling, dashboards, and stacked) <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2997\">#2997</a>.</li>\n<li>10x faster opening of large notebooks <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2334\">#2334</a>.</li>\n<li>Fixed time plot labels <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3061\">#3061</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3052\">#3052</a>.</li>\n<li>Portable version for Windows, run self-contained on thumb drive <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2779\">#2779</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix server disconnection problem <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2946\">#2946</a>.</li>\n<li>Added Sublime code editing key bindings option <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2993\">#2993</a>.</li>\n<li>Plotly works in R without iframe <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3053\">#3053</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix Scala on Windows <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3292\">#3292</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix Kdb on Windows <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/3371\">#3371</a>.</li>\n<li>Many fixes for Electron versions.</li>\n<li>For a complete list of the 447 resolved issues, see <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed+closed%3A2015-10-01..2016-01-17\">github</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-4-2-2015-10-20\">1.4.2 - 2015.10.20</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix IRuby backend in Docker <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2644\">#2644</a>.</li>\n<li>Allow unlisted publications <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2588\">#2588</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix handling of Groovy [null] <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2646\">#2646</a>.</li>\n<li>Raised autotranslation limit to 16MB <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/pull/2652\">#2652</a>.</li>\n<li>Fixed Auto-complete on Windows in Groovy <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2687\">#2687</a>.</li>\n<li>Improve error reporting on Python version mismatch <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2723\">#2723</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix link to documentation on case-sensitive filesystems <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2749\">#2749</a>.</li>\n<li>On Windows, allow saving to drives other than C: <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2685\">#2685</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix section numbering in hierarchy view <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2689\">#2689</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-4-1-2015-10-06\">1.4.1 - 2015.10.06</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix Python in Docker container <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2591\">#2591</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix language prefs path on Windows <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2622\">#2622</a>.</li>\n<li>LaTeX not enabled by default <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2618\">#2618</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix Windows Electron process leak <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2555\">#2555</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-4-2015-10-01\">1.4 - 2015.10.01</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Support <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560b4ea6-5a57-4298-84e3-a3057c1ee4b4?fullscreen=true\">C++</a> and <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560b4a2f-546b-4929-acd7-0d47365b896e?fullscreen=true\">SQL</a>.</li>\n<li>Support <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560cb7e9-68b4-4659-9863-ce5d6ce93dd4?fullscreen=true\">Scala Spark</a>.</li>\n<li>Support <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560d93db-8940-42aa-aeb0-b0fd1af81b3b?fullscreen=true\">IPython widgets</a>.</li>\n<li>Support <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560ca254-071b-4647-8073-c4f941ca02e8?fullscreen=true\">ggvis</a> and <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560ca17d-b941-4607-8f8e-dd2d5820a131?fullscreen=true\">bokeh</a>.</li>\n<li>New <a href=\"http://pub.beakernotebook.com\">publication server</a>.</li>\n<li>Add <a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560ca655-12df-43b9-9ecd-5714766b8fc4?fullscreen=true\">EasyForm API</a>.</li>\n<li>Many improvements to the native <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1458\">time-series plotting API</a>.</li>\n<li>New experimental native <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/wiki/Electron-Beaker\">Electron builds</a>.</li>\n<li>Supports IPython 4.0 protocol (except we have a regression of <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2591\">4.0 and Docker</a>, so watch for 1.4.1).</li>\n<li>Consistent use the <a href=\"https://www.google.com/fonts/specimen/Roboto+Mono\">Roboto Mono typeface</a> for code.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pub.beakernotebook.com/publications/560b54da-3c14-4890-8b64-b204bc798320?fullscreen=true\">Template expansion</a> in text cells.</li>\n<li>Improved UI for <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1799#issuecomment-145197219\">inserting cells</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved UI for <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/470#issuecomment-128892348\">hierarchy view</a>.</li>\n<li>New key command to evaluate code line-by-line, or evaluate any selected snippet of code <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2181\">#2181</a>.</li>\n<li>Support for displaying <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1501#issuecomment-145198624\">docstrings</a> in Python.</li>\n<li>For a complete list of the 341 resolved issues, see <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed+closed%3A2015-07-01..2015-10-01\">github</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-3-4-2015-08-07\">1.3.4 - 2015.08.07</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix compatibility with IPython 3.2.1 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2003\">#2003</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix R outputing graphics and value at the same time <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2020\">#2020</a>.</li>\n<li>Update Ruby to work with latest version <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1990\">#1990</a>.</li>\n<li>Allow iframes in HTML <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1925\">#1925</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-3-3-2015-07-24\">1.3.3 - 2015.07.24</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix IPython in Safari <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1952\">#1952</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-3-2-2015-07-11\">1.3.2 - 2015.07.11</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix R in the Docker Container <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1918\">#1918</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-3-1-2015-06-26\">1.3.1 - 2015.06.26</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Documentation improvements, especially the dashboard tutorial.</li>\n<li>Fix tab at beginning of line <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1862\">#1862</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix Scala class loader concurrency bug <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1855\">#1855</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-3-2015-06-26\">1.3 - 2015.06.26</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Support PySpark and SparkR <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1521\">#1521</a>.</li>\n<li>Support Clojure and Kdb.</li>\n<li>Autotranslation improvements such as autodecting date/times, dataframes, images, etc <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/522\">#522</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1412\">#1412</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1522\">#1522</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1525\">#1525</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1664\">#1664</a>.</li>\n<li>New directory for generating files you can access from HTML. <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/708\">#708</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1371\">#1371</a>.</li>\n<li>New editor for text cells and section headers, adding inline math, and fixing bugs with special characters and supporting vim mode <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/125\">#125</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/555\">#555</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/704\">#704</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1315\">#1315</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1345\">#1345</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1362\">1362</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1407\">#1407</a>.</li>\n<li>New data frame interface, including column formatting options <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/818\">#818</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1270\">#1270</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1279\">#1279</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1437\">#1437</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1599\">#1599</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1668\">#1668</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1715\">#1715</a>.</li>\n<li>New insert cell button in advanced mode <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1241\">#1241</a>.</li>\n<li>Restore IRuby <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1129\">#1129</a>.</li>\n<li>IPython handle laptops going to sleep. <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1576\">#1576</a>.</li>\n<li>Allow editing default imports of Python <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1188\">#1188</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved JavaScript stack traces <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/889\">#889</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1357\">#1357</a>.</li>\n<li>Add printing to cell output from JavaScript <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/333\">#333</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved key-bindings, autoindent, and autocomplete <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1365\">#1365</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1467\">#1467</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1468\">#1468</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1505\">#1505</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1649\">#1649</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1661\">#1661</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1670\">#1670</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1773\">#1773</a>.</li>\n<li>Much faster math (TeX) rendering via KaTeX <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/698\">#698</a>.</li>\n<li>Handle very large charts from R <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1540\">#1540</a>.</li>\n<li>Better handling of output from R <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1612\">#1612</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1622\">#1622</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved vertical density, especially of advanced mode <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/578\">#578</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1360\">#1360</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1483\">#1483</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1565\">#1565</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1566\">#1566</a>.</li>\n<li>Increase and improve the included tutorial documentation, and the website <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1400\">#1400</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1528\">#1528</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1604\">#1604</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1642\">#1642</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1775\">#1775</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1784\">#1784</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1785\">#1785</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1833\">#1833</a>.</li>\n<li>Misc UI and layout <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/455\">#455</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/569\">#569</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/577\">#577</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/676\">#676</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1200\">#1200</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1363\">#1363</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1382\">#1382</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1408\">#1403</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1420\">#1420</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1421\">#1421</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1422\">#1422</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1423\">#1423</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1430\">#1430</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1493\">#1493</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1494\">#1494</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1568\">#1568</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1571\">#1571</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1574\">#1574</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1608\">#1608</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1627\">#1627</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1631\">#1631</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1646\">#1646</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1675\">#1675</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1737\">#1737</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1774\">#1774</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1807\">#1807</a>.</li>\n<li>Fixed cookies leak that caused IPython to stop working after extended use <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/750\">#750</a>.</li>\n<li>Add attribution page as required by some licenses <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1733\">#1733</a>.</li>\n<li>Infrastructure improvements like concatenating the JS into fewer files, and upgrading from Java 7 to 8 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/409\">#409</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/897\">#897</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1229\">#1229</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1384\">#1384</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1388\">#1388</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1445\">#1445</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1463\">#1463</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1600\">#1600</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1619\">#1619</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1703\">#1703</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1734\">#1734</a>.</li>\n<li>JQuery creates circular notebook and crashes <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/891\">#891</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1409\">#1409</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix proxy confusion, limit authentication headers <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1366\">#1366</a>.</li>\n<li>Other fixes: <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1438\">#1438</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1484\">#1484</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1485\">#1485</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1503\">#1503</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1678\">#1678</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1691\">#1691</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1711\">#1711</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-2-1-2015-03-29\">1.2.1 - 2015.03.29</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix Autocompletion when using IPython3 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1351\">#1351</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-2-2015-03-27\">1.2 - 2015.03.27</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Support Scala and Java, including sharing classes with Groovy.</li>\n<li>Support running Python2 and Python3 at the same time, even with different versions of IPython <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/776\">#776</a>.</li>\n<li>Allow user to select location of language backend from their beaker.prefs.json file, as well as the options passed to it <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1166\">#1166</a>.</li>\n<li>Works with IPython3 (in addtion to 1 and 2) <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1222\">#1222</a>.</li>\n<li>Works with Mac OS 10.6 and 10.7 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/408\">#408</a>.</li>\n<li>Works on Macs with old chipsets <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/398\">#398</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/982\">#982</a>.</li>\n<li>Better error reporting from missing backend <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1180\">#1180</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/880\">#880</a>, </li>\n<li>New API for progress reporting during cell evaluation <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/910\">#910</a>.</li>\n<li>New API for fullscreen dashboards <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1025\">#1025</a>.</li>\n<li>New API for reflection (access to other cells source code and results) and control (cell evaluation can trigger evaluation of other cells).</li>\n<li>Standard output and error output now appear below the cell that produced them instead of in a unified panel <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/667\">#667</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/937\">#937</a>.</li>\n<li>Add tutorial for loading external JavaScript libraries, in particular p5.js <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1176\">#1176</a>.</li>\n<li>Allow sharing and saving <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> elements <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1075\">#1075</a>.</li>\n<li>Handle installation and user paths with spaces <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/931\">#931</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix JavaScript injection problem on shared notebooks <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/862\">#862</a>.</li>\n<li>New View menu item &quot;close all sections&quot; <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/872\">#872</a>.</li>\n<li>Upload notebooks with native file dialog or drag-and-drop <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/830\">#830</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/857\">#857</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1116\">#1116</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved Language Manager UI.</li>\n<li>Use scss to improve modularity of styles <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1071\">#1071</a>.</li>\n<li>Support ipynb section headings during import <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1015\">#1015</a>.</li>\n<li>Subsections numbered from 1 instead of 0 <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/629\">#629</a>.</li>\n<li>Groovy evaluation is interruptible <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/560\">#560</a>.</li>\n<li>Add progress indicator to sharing <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/383\">#383</a>.</li>\n<li>UI for tagging cells <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/403\">#403</a>.</li>\n<li>R plots made with ggplot2 work on Firefox <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/987\">#987</a></li>\n<li>On Windows find R via the registry instead of the PATH <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1178\">#1178</a>.</li>\n<li>Improved file open and save dialogs <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/904\">#904</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1016\">#1016</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1017\">#1017</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1061\">#1061</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1158\">#1158</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1159\">#1159</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1161\">#1161</a>.</li>\n<li>Massive UI polish <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/672\">#672</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/673\">#673</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/747\">#747</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/772\">#772</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/819\">#819</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/854\">#854</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/856\">#856</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/874\">#874</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/902\">#902</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/906\">#906</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/968\">#968</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/970\">#970</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/972\">#972</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/990\">#990</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1027\">#1027</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1045\">#1045</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1047\">#1047</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1053\">#1053</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1062\">#1062</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1070\">#1070</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1119\">#1119</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1130\">#1130</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1139\">#1139</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-1-2-2014-11-5\">1.1.2 - 2014.11.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix problem where a missing backend prevents the whole notebook from loading <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/836\">#836</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/845\">#845</a></li>\n<li>And on 2014.11.11 made a new build of windows, still version 1.1.2 but packaged correctly to fix <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/853\">#853</a></li>\n<li>And on 2015.01.16 made a new build of mac, still version 1.1.2 but with a hotfix for <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/824\">#824</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-1-1-2014-10-31\">1.1.1 - 2014.10.31</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix problem with defining functions in R <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/827\">#827</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-1-2014-10-30\">1.1 - 2014.10.30</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New table (dataframe) display <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/716\">#716</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/717\">#717</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/735\">#735</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/432\">#432</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/270\">#270</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/760\">#760</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/777\">#777</a></li>\n<li>Able to open larger notebooks without freezing by loading plugins before rendering the notebook (however the downside of this is you can&#39;t see the notebook while the plugins load) <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/pull/751\">#751</a></li>\n<li>Most keyboard commands (especially command-enter to run the current cell) can now be accessed with command key, not just control (for Mac users) <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/220\">#220</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/778\">#778</a></li>\n<li>Python3 support <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/695\">#695</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/740\">#740</a></li>\n<li>Direct access to autotranslation in python without a function call (<code>beaker.x</code> instead of <code>beaker.get(&quot;x&quot;)</code>) <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/675\">#675</a></li>\n<li>Add the ability to control the size of R plots <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/707\">#707</a></li>\n<li>Correctly suppress invisible results from R <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/232\">#232</a></li>\n<li>Add the ability to share d3 plots <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/691\">#691</a></li>\n<li>Replace the d3 tutorial, various tutorial polish <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/685\">#685</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/729\">#729</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/730\">#730</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/732\">#732</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/754\">#754</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/790\">#790</a></li>\n<li>Do not hide &quot;falsey&quot; evaluation results <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/444\">#444</a></li>\n<li>Fixed Docker container port remapping and Python plugin <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/702\">#702</a></li>\n<li>Sharing server now supports levels of detail and section toggling</li>\n<li>Sharing server URL location is configurable <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/769\">#769</a></li>\n<li>Fixed display of dataframes in python mangled by pandas groupby operation <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/694\">#694</a></li>\n<li>Interaction state of plots and tables saved in the notebook and shareable <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/413\">#413</a></li>\n<li>Remove deprecated --pylab option from IPython <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/165\">#165</a></li>\n<li>When loading a plugin from a cross-origin URL, show a dialog warning the user that it could be unsafe <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/144\">#144</a></li>\n<li>Better cache busting method (so you should not have to clear the cache when you upgrade Beaker) <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/742\">#742</a></li>\n<li>Changed short name of Groovy from Gr to Gv <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/687\">#687</a></li>\n<li>Avoid Java icon in dock <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/688\">#688</a></li>\n<li>Improve plot handling of NaNs <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/697\">#697</a></li>\n<li>New icon, favicon, and branding <a href=\"https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/755\">#755</a></li>\n<li>Update JRE from 7u60 to 7u71</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1-0-2014-09-24\">1.0 - 2014.09.24</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Redesigned UI that is beautiful and easier to use.</li>\n<li>Autotranslation of data between languages.</li>\n<li>Interactive charting, including with levels-of-detail.</li>\n<li>Docker container for easy deployment.</li>\n<li>Detect when connection to server is lost and give extra chance to\nsave the notebook.</li>\n<li>Plugin manager allows removing languages from a notebook.</li>\n<li>Security fix for Julia on multiuser systems.</li>\n<li>Removed Ruby from plugin manager because it is insecure on\nmultiuser systems (but it can still be added by entering its URL).</li>\n<li>Rewrite tutorials.</li>\n<li>Numerous bug fixes.</li>\n<li>Groovy supports classpath to access JARS, and default imports.</li>\n<li>R supports interrupting evaluations.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"0-55-2014-07-17\">0.55 - 2014.07.17</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Major upgrade of the security model: backends are now protected even on multi-user systems.</li>\n<li>Add public server option so that you can access Beaker over the internet, not just locally. Includes HTTPS encryption.</li>\n<li>Refactor the JavaScript to conform to Angular guidelines.</li>\n<li>Improve file load/save dialogs to be easier to use and handle errors.</li>\n<li>Shared notebooks can be downloaded from the resulting share page, and the sharing viewer can open a notebook file hosted anywhere.</li>\n<li>On Mac, add a native application to wrap and launch the web app. The native app includes the JRE, eliminating an external dependency for users.</li>\n<li>On Windows, include the JRE, nginx, and python in our distribution.</li>\n<li>On Ubuntu, include a script to install all dependencies and language plugins.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"0-52-4-2014-05-03\">0.52.4 - 2014.05.03</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Security fix: close ports to external access.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"0-52-1-2014-05-02\">0.52.1 - 2014.05.02</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix loading nginx dynamic libraries on Mac.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"0-52-2014-04-29\">0.52 - 2014.04.29</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First public release.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>");;return buf.join("");
